 <h3><%=intl._("IP and Transport Configuration")%></h3><p>
 <b><%=intl._("The default settings will work for most people.")%>
 <a href="#chelp"><%=intl._("There is help below.")%></a></b>
 </p><p><b><%=intl._("UPnP Configuration")%>:</b><br>
